At 08:07 PM 12/8/97 -0500, you wrote:

>Has anyone (Drexler, et al) addressed Dr. Smalley's objection to the

>feasibility of MNT?

>

>His problem is with thermal resolution and can be found at

>http://cnst.rice.edu/NanoWelch.html

